With this beautiful product, you can charge your phone in an eco-friendly way with no cost to you or the environment. Along with being durable, nylon also ensures that this backpack can survive rugged outdoor use, thus you can confidently wear this bag while you are out camping. This backpack is also water-resistant and keeps your laptop safe in wet and damp conditions. The Sunlast laptop backpack is perfect for your laptop. This backpack features top loading and can accommodate a large size laptop easily.
